Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.33,0:00:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[新机动战记-钢弹W]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.37,0:00:34.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使受了伤也无妨  不转移目光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.37,0:00:40.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想热切、激烈地生存下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.37,0:00:48.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,给我永不放弃的坚强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.37,0:00:53.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想紧紧抱着你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.37,0:00:56.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I JUST FEEL "RHYTHM EMOTION"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.37,0:01:00.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,过去或痛楚都
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.37,0:01:06.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,引导至鲜明的、一瞬间的光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.37,0:01:10.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I JUST FEEL "RHYTHM EMOTION"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.37,0:01:13.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我胸中的鼓励
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.37,0:01:19.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,向你延续而去  SO FARAWAY...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.01,0:01:30.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,罗姆斐拉财团藉着邀请和平的象征
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.52,0:01:32.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜‧匹斯克拉福特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.25,0:01:34.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作为财团的代表
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.32,0:01:35.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,得到人们的支持
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.99,0:01:38.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功实现了世界国家的构想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.29,0:01:45.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,另一方面，在宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.16,0:01:47.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,名为白色獠牙的武装集团
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.67,0:01:51.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,寻求卫星独立，揭竿起义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.14,0:01:59.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,白色獠牙成功邀得新领导人加入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.18,0:02:05.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地球和宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.05,0:02:09.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这两个个体会产生对立
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.12,0:02:12.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的名字是米利亚尔特‧匹斯克拉福特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.26,0:02:14.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和宇宙对立的个体，地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.59,0:02:17.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在这里宣布要肃清它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.97,0:02:24.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杰克斯\N从次代显示的未来里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.00,0:02:27.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你选择了那条路吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.54,0:02:29.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从飞翼零式显示的未来里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.57,0:02:31.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我选择了的是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.84,0:02:34.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这条路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.12,0:02:40.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第四十一话\N[巴尔吉攻防战]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.89,0:02:44.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敌人MD\N突破宇宙机雷群
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.56,0:02:47.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,120秒后和防卫线接触
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.06,0:02:48.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,MD陶拉斯部队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.89,0:02:50.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,展开防卫队型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.50,0:02:52.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,30秒后布阵完毕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.30,0:02:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巴尔吉炮怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.23,0:02:57.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,连接工程完毕，收容工程组
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.50,0:03:00.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加快注入能量   是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.10,0:03:02.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全体第三级战斗部署
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.61,0:03:05.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,陶拉斯全部出动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.51,0:03:07.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别让敌人接近巴尔吉这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.88,0:03:09.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里是宇宙最后一个堡垒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.81,0:03:11.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可战败
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.62,0:03:15.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雷射炮对比尔哥无效
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.65,0:03:18.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让它们拿所有雷射炮出击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.09,0:03:20.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,仍未调整出力，会容易过热
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.96,0:03:21.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要紧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.93,0:03:24.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少许也好，减少敌人数目就行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.33,0:03:30.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敌人MD
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.54,0:03:32.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,距离和第一防卫线接触还有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.37,0:03:36.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,10，9，8，7，6
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.47,0:03:40.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,5，4，3，2，1
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.35,0:03:44.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,战斗开始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.79,0:03:55.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,白色獠牙的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.09,0:03:58.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙要塞巴尔吉攻略战开始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.53,0:04:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在这场战斗里胜出的一方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.03,0:04:02.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就会掌握宇宙的霸权
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.00,0:04:05.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这方面谁都清楚知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.04,0:04:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此，OZ宇宙军和白色獠牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.24,0:04:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把所有军力投入这场战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.94,0:04:14.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,攻防战非常激烈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.28,0:04:22.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,MD第5中队在左翼布阵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.95,0:04:26.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,侵入敌人防卫线35%
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.16,0:04:29.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，就此攻进去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.53,0:04:31.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有物体从后方接近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.53,0:04:32.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.83,0:04:35.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是?次代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.03,0:04:37.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米利亚尔特司令吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.70,0:04:41.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请等等，米利亚尔特司令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.51,0:04:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你为何驾驶机动战士出击?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.54,0:04:46.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是白色獠牙的司令官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.08,0:04:47.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,交由MD战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.01,0:04:49.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在后方指挥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.61,0:04:51.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那交给你负责
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.89,0:04:59.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他仍然打算做闪电伯爵吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.94,0:05:13.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请等等  诺茵小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.91,0:05:16.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道我很任性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.54,0:05:17.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.64,0:05:20.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我无论如何一定要见杰克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.24,0:05:22.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杰克斯有他的主意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.81,0:05:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他的行动应该是为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.91,0:05:26.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜殿下和山克王国着想的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.82,0:05:27.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尽管如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.85,0:05:30.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你独自去巴尔吉太危险了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.52,0:05:32.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沙漠钢弹的修理也完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.82,0:05:34.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也和你一起去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.89,0:05:36.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特尔?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.86,0:05:41.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巴尔吉周围也有很多民间卫星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.10,0:05:44.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不被他们发觉潜入去很简单啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.17,0:05:45.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迪欧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.47,0:05:47.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你和我们一起去吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.34,0:05:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也想向OZ和白色獠牙的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.74,0:05:53.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大肆宣传死神的复活啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.28,0:05:56.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多谢你，迪欧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.11,0:05:58.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就连他…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.78,0:06:01.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也能掩护你们吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.49,0:06:03.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.49,0:06:05.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.19,0:06:07.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，决定了就快点启程吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.69,0:06:09.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.89,0:06:36.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敌人全军覆没
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.55,0:06:38.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,基地镇压完毕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.46,0:06:44.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的敌人在宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.57,0:06:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莎莉‧普奥?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.84,0:06:59.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看来赶得及呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.65,0:07:05.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请等等，这部机里有重要的货物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.75,0:07:07.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难得我找它出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.35,0:07:09.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,毁了它很可惜吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.53,0:07:24.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛，你打算回宇宙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.90,0:07:27.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么，你可以带这部机体回去吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.12,0:07:40.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你知道特洛瓦的所在了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.18,0:07:44.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我认为这时代需要钢弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.46,0:07:45.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.99,0:07:49.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它们的驾驶员是能够信任的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.29,0:07:52.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以，我也想尽力而为啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.53,0:07:57.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛，你们的战斗太孤独了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.57,0:07:59.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不喜欢被同情吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.97,0:08:01.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但请你让我帮你一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.61,0:08:06.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有敌人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.21,0:08:08.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你准备穿俊机出发
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.75,0:08:10.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里由我应付
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.48,0:08:15.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敌人在哪里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.66,0:08:23.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那孩子好像稍微改变了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.26,0:08:25.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他以前就像一柄磨利的刀一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.36,0:08:27.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难以接近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.37,0:08:31.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加快把钢弹运进穿梭机里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.45,0:08:51.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底怎么回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.46,0:08:53.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,继承匹斯克拉福特血脉的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.89,0:08:56.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然要自相残杀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.76,0:08:58.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伟列兹公爵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.46,0:09:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他真的是\N米利亚尔特‧匹斯克拉福特吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.83,0:09:05.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不想相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.10,0:09:07.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，不会有错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.47,0:09:10.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜女王有何打算?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.77,0:09:12.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迪尔麦优侯爵身亡后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.28,0:09:14.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能团结开始改革的罗姆斐拉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.65,0:09:17.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有莉莉娜殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.21,0:09:21.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已故的匹斯克拉福特国王  对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.29,0:09:24.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们为了理想带领你的孩子们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.29,0:09:27.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,步进残酷的命运里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.29,0:09:29.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你们真的那样想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.36,0:09:31.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们就服从我的意见吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.02,0:10:01.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在，地球好不容易\N正步向和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.03,0:10:05.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但王兄究竟在打什么主意?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.73,0:10:11.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，即使王兄有何打算也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.17,0:10:13.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,战斗是错的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.47,0:10:16.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,制止战斗是我的任务
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.80,0:10:42.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有人吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.24,0:10:54.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,久违了，莉莉娜小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.61,0:10:57.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯‧克修里那达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.28,0:10:58.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你为何会在这里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.68,0:11:02.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想罗姆斐拉最高会议的决定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.09,0:11:03.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,转告给你知道呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.79,0:11:05.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,财团的决定?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.59,0:11:08.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从今日起革去\N莉莉娜‧匹斯克拉福特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.46,0:11:11.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,罗姆斐拉财团代表的身份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.66,0:11:14.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你退下女王的宝座吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.04,0:11:24.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.64,0:11:27.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我把罗姆斐拉的权力还给你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.04,0:11:30.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，在那之前\N我有工作要做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.95,0:11:32.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想说服哥哥米利亚尔特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.75,0:11:35.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,制止他和地球敌对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.79,0:11:40.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那件事你做不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.66,0:11:43.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么意思?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.16,0:11:47.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把你关在罗姆斐拉\N这个古老雀笼里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.10,0:11:48.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是一种罪恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.00,0:11:52.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么，我就成为罗姆斐拉的代表
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.57,0:11:55.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由我的手了结一切吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.31,0:12:01.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去你想去的地方吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.51,0:12:04.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是自由的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.27,0:12:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜殿下要去宇宙呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.54,0:12:30.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么，我也要准备穿梭机呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.09,0:13:26.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,始终是没有生命的木偶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.76,0:13:28.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是我的对手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.90,0:13:34.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可恶的钢弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.27,0:13:37.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎可以再被他们突破防卫线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.17,0:13:39.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,准备发射巴尔吉的主炮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.51,0:13:42.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，能量注入率还是80%
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.88,0:13:45.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要紧!就那样发射
