Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.22,0:16:39.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们认真的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.99,0:16:42.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被那种东西击中\N卫星会毁灭啊
