Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.92,0:17:48.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再次准备发射巴尔吉炮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.13,0:17:50.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下一击要把他们全部消灭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.70,0:17:58.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样下去…
