Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.66,0:18:25.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们去阻止巴尔吉炮发射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.70,0:18:27.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是…  快去
