Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.47,0:19:07.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地球才是战争的根源
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.57,0:19:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是…
