Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.86,0:22:15.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,待续
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.54,0:22:30.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心血来潮的找人出来\N只因为天气好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.84,0:22:38.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让我一直等不到人\N你以为你是谁
